**Project**: cfd-harness-unified
**Trigger**: RETRO-V61-001 risk-tier (multi-file backend + new HTTP surface + frontend dispatch + new transcoding/parsing logic, ~2329 LOC)
**Spec**: `.planning/strategic/m_render_api_kickoff/spec_v2_2026-04-28.md` (read this first — defines acceptance criteria)
**DEC**: `.planning/decisions/2026-04-28_v61_095_m_render_api_kickoff.md`
