## Arc structure

| Step | Commit | Subject |
|------|--------|---------|
| 2+3 | d0360bf | services/render skeleton + /geometry/render glb + mtime cache |
| 4   | 676b8c2 | /mesh/render polyMesh wireframe glb (hand-built minimal glTF LINES) |
