(M-RENDER-API B.2 · DEC-V61-095 spec_v2 §B.2).

A unit-cube polyMesh has 8 points, 6 quad faces, and 12 unique edges;
that's the canonical fixture used across the parser, edge extractor,
glTF builder, and the route.
